OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening, with plenty of late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Mostly clear overnight,
OL,8,Fbecoming rather cool in rural parts.
OL,9,FRemaining breezy, especially over
OL,10,Fhills and coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Fresh easterly winds, these
OL,14,Fstrong over hills. Warm inland but
OL,15,Ffeeling cooler along coasts and over
OL,16,Fhills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
