OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday and Friday, dry with long
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Breezy Thursday, easing
OL,8,FFriday. Cloudier Saturday with sunny
OL,9,Fintervals and an increasing risk of
OL,10,Fshowers. Temperatures increasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
